data.title: FEMALE Definition & Meaning
data.meta_description: Female definition: having or relating to a gender identity that corresponds to a complex, variable set of social and cultural roles, traits, and behaviors assigned to people of the sex that typically produces egg cells. . See examples of FEMALE used in a sentence.
